Coordinated Care

When you choose Northwest Healthcare

for emergency and urgent care services, you help

ensure physicians have immediate access to

your medical records for better follow-up and care

coordination.

Learn More

Could a Bariatric Procedure

Be Your New Beginning?

If you struggle with obesity, and traditional weight-loss options

have failed, a bariatric procedure might be a good option for you.

Find out if you're a candidate now.

Wellness Visits

your annual Medicare Wellness Visit. It's an

important part of your preventive care!

Schedule Now
